  "texts": [
    "Note enrichment.",
    "The contexts in the gold-standard dataset are clinical notes that contain some IDU-related information.",
    "As such, we select a cohort of patients whose notes have a higher chance of containing IDUrelated information, such as patients who have been diagnosed with Hepatitis C. To guarantee that the clinical notes include information relevant to IDU and narrow down the notes accordingly, we use a list of keywords/phrases that are indicative of IDU (refer to Table 2) and has been developed by SMEs.",
    "SMEs followed an iterative approach to create this list.",
    "They began by compiling a list of common terms related to IDU, which they then refined by reviewing the associated snippet."
